    <title><![CDATA[Android变色状态栏]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.nuttysoft.com/2016/01/16/Android%E5%8F%98%E8%89%B2%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E6%A0%8F/"/>
    <id>http://www.nuttysoft.com/2016/01/16/Android变色状态栏/</id>
    <published>2016-01-16T13:28:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-01-16T14:23:53.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>  以前的时候把平时搜集的资料都放在了印象笔记和为知笔记里面，为了治疗懒癌，有必要把笔记的东西翻出来了。造福自己，帮助他人。</p>
<p>  今天介绍一个android的开源库用来实现变色状态栏。有关于沉浸式和透明状态栏的区别，请自行搜索。</p>
<p>  补上该库的传送门：<a href="https://github.com/jgilfelt/SystemBarTint" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/jgilfelt/SystemBarTint</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h3 id="u6DFB_u52A0_u4F9D_u8D56"><a href="#u6DFB_u52A0_u4F9D_u8D56" class="headerlink" title="添加依赖"></a>添加依赖</h3><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dependencies &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    compile <span class="string">'com.readystatesoftware.systembartint:systembartint:1.0.3'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="u521B_u5EFA_u62D3_u5C55_u51FD_u6570"><a href="#u521B_u5EFA_u62D3_u5C55_u51FD_u6570" class="headerlink" title="创建拓展函数"></a>创建拓展函数</h3><p>  因为kotlin支持拓展函数，所以用拓展函数实现。java版本自行脑补。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fun Activity.changeStatusBar(res: Int)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//不小于4.4版本设置透明状态栏</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(Build.VERSION.SDK_INT &gt;= Build.VERSION_CODES.KITKAT)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        var win: Window = <span class="keyword">this</span>.window</span><br><span class="line">        var winParams: WindowManager.LayoutParams = win.attributes</span><br><span class="line">        val bits : Int = WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_TRANSLUCENT_STATUS</span><br><span class="line">        winParams.flags = bits</span><br><span class="line">        win.attributes = winParams</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//获取管理器</span></span><br><span class="line">    var tinManager: SystemBarTintManager = SystemBarTintManager(<span class="keyword">this</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//允许状态栏变色</span></span><br><span class="line">    tinManager.isStatusBarTintEnabled = <span class="keyword">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//设置颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">    tinManager.setStatusBarTintResource(res)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样Activity就有一个叫做chageStatusBar的方法了，建议将这个拓展方法放在特定的拓展类下面，就像我门给帮助方法建一个帮助类一样。当然，你也可以把他放在你乐意放的地方。<br>之后在你自己的Activity的onCreate方法中调用changeStatus(R.color.xxx)</p>
<h3 id="u7ED9_u5E03_u5C40_u6587_u4EF6_u6DFB_u52A0_u5C5E_u6027"><a href="#u7ED9_u5E03_u5C40_u6587_u4EF6_u6DFB_u52A0_u5C5E_u6027" class="headerlink" title="给布局文件添加属性"></a>给布局文件添加属性</h3><p>将下面的内容添加套布局根节点中，这样，你的布局就不会顶到“天上”去了。</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">android:clipToPadding="true"</span><br><span class="line">android:fitsSystemWindows="true"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>完成上面的步骤，你的状态栏就变成了R.color.xxx的颜色了。java版本的也不难写出来。</p>
]]></content>
